quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  21,51,"Ampa sε Ye’dii kan de Abraham kwankyerε maa no, na na Ye’nim no yie (fa negyidie ho)"
  21,52,"Ɛberε a ͻka kyerεε na’gya ne nenkorͻfoͻ sε: “Ɛdeεn ne saa ahonin a mode moho ama resom wͻn yi?”"
  21,53,"Wͻ’buaa sε: “Yε’bεtoo Yε’agyanom sε wͻ’resom wͻn"
  21,54,"Ɔkaa sε: “Ampa sε mo ne moagya nom (nyinaa) wͻ ͻyera pefee mu paa“"
  21,55,"Wͻ’kaa sε: “Wode nokorε na aberε yεn anaasε woka wͻn a wͻ’di fεw no ho?”"
  21,56,"Abraham kaa sε: “Daabi, Mo Wura Nyankopͻn no, Ɔne ͻsoro ne asaase Wura a Ɔbͻͻ (soro ne asaase) no, na medeε meka wͻn a wͻ’di woi ho adanseε no ho"
  21,57,"“Medͻ Nyame sε: “Ansa na mobεkͻ adane moakyi asan aba no, na m’abͻ moabosom no ho pͻ (asεe no) “"
  21,58,"Enti obubuu (abosom no) asinasin, na mmom (ogyaa) wͻn mu kεseε no sεdeε wͻ’bεsan abεto no"
  21,59,"(Wͻ’behunuiε no) wͻ’kaa sε: “Hwan na wayε yεn anyame yi seyie? Nokorε sε (saa nipa no), ka abͻneεfoͻ no ho “"
  21,60,"Wͻ’kekaa sε: “Yε’tee sε abranteε bi rekeka wͻn ho asεm (bɔne), yεfrε no Abraham”"
  21,61,"Wͻ’kaa sε: “Monfa no mmra nnipa no anim sεdeε wͻ’bedi ho adanseε ”"
  21,62,"Wͻ’bisaa sε: “Abraham wo na woyεε yεn anyame no seyie yi?”"
  21,63,"Abraham kaa sε: “Daabi, wͻn mu (bosom) kεseε woi na ayε, enti sε (abosom no) kasa a, εneε momisa wͻn“"
  21,64,"Enti wͻ’dwenee ho wͻ wͻn ara wͻn mu, na wͻ’kekaa sε: “Nokorε sε moka abͻneεfoͻ no ho “"
  21,65,"Aniwuo maa wͻ’sisii wͻn ti ase (kaa sε): “(Abraham), wonim yie sε (abosom) woi nom nnkasa “"
  21,66,Abraham kaa sε “Enti mofri Nyankopͻn akyi som adeε a entumi mma mo mfasoͻ biara na entumi mfa ͻhaw biara nso mma mo?”
  21,67,“Moani awu wͻ deε mofri Nyankopͻn akyi som no ho. Enti monni adwen?”
  21,68,"Wͻ’kaa sε: “Monhye no na mommoa mo anyame, sε mobԑyε (no biribi) a"
  21,69,"Yε’kaa sε: ”Egya, yε nyunu ne asomdweε ma Abraham “"
  21,70,Wͻ’hwehwεε sε wͻ’bͻ (Abraham) ho pͻ bͻne enti Yε’maa wͻ’yεε berεguofoͻ
  21,71,Yε’gyee Abraham ne Lut nso nkwa de wͻn kͻͻ asaase a Y’ahyira so ama amansan no so
  21,72,"Na Yε’de Is’haaq kyεε no, εna (Yε’yεε) Ya’aquub nso ntosoͻ (maa no), na Yε’maa wͻn mu biara yεε nipa papa"
  21,73,"Yε’yεε wͻn akandifoͻ a wͻ’de Y’ahyεdeε no kyerε (amanfoͻ) kwan, na Ye’yii papayε ne Nyamefrε ne Zaka yie maa wͻn, na (Yεnko ara na na) wͻ’som Yεn"
  21,74,"Lut nso Yε’maa no nyansa ne nimdeε, na Yε’gyee no fri kuro no a na wͻ’yε akyiwadeε no mu. Nokorε sε na wͻ’yε nnipa bͻnefoͻ, ahohwifoͻ"
  21,75,Yε’de no wuraa Y’ahummͻborͻ no mu. Nokorε sε na ͻka apapafoͻ no ho